APIs
Application Programming Interface

A  - When application have to interact to each other with different it does through APIs
P  - Through APIs one piece of code can interact with another piece of code ( diff programming language )
I  - Interface ( Abstraction )

Advantages
    Communication
    Abstraction
    Platform Agnostic

Example Of APIs
    Private APIs - Hidden APIs
    Public APIs  - google map, stripe api
    Web APIs     - Application of running on cloud interact with each other
    SDK/LibraryAPIs - Abstraction

API Factors
    API contract
    Documentation
    Data Format
    Security

API Standards
    RPC   - Remote Processor Call
    SOAP  - Simple object access protocol
    REST  - Representational State Transfer